5. Updates the mutable variable using `mutableVar.set(baseValue + delta)`
6. Gets the updated sum using `sumCalc.get()` again
7. Returns the result with both initial and updated sums

The reactive system will automatically propagate the change from the mutable variable to the calculation, ensuring the updated sum reflects the new value.

